Dialogue: 100,0:00:09.11,0:00:11.11,Default - Top,Teacher,0,0,0,,The sports festival is coming up soon.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:11.11,0:00:15.62,Default - Top,Teacher,0,0,0,,Be sure to show your parents the notice I just handed out.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:17.53,0:00:20.37,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Saikawa, what's a sports festival?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.37,0:00:23.75,Default,S,0,0,0,,Oh, they didn't have them in your country?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:23.75,0:00:27.38,Default,S,0,0,0,,A sports festival is a super fun event.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:27.38,0:00:28.46,Default,S,0,0,0,,You run...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:28.46,0:00:29.46,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Run?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.46,0:00:30.63,Default,S,0,0,0,,Throw balls...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.63,0:00:31.76,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Throw balls?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:31.76,0:00:32.92,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,Pull ropes...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.92,0:00:34.18,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Pull ropes?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:34.18,0:00:37.30,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,And all kinds of other fun stuff as we \Nwork together as a class and try to win!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.43,0:00:41.22,Default,S,0,0,0,,Our moms and dads come to watch too.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.48,Default,S,0,0,0,,We even get to eat lunch with them!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.31,0:00:48.56,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,You're super athletic, \Nso I bet you'll be the star of the show.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.56,0:00:51.32,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,And then your mom will praise you!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.28,0:00:56.78,Default,K,0,0,0,,I've got work that day. Can't.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:28.96,0:02:32.50,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Take the day off, Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.50,0:02:34.17,Default,K,0,0,0,,It's not that easy.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.17,0:02:38.17,Default,T,0,0,0,joined,Kanna, Miss Kobayashi might end up \Nfacing Hades during her death march.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.88,0:02:40.47,Default,T,0,0,0,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.47,0:02:41.05,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.80,0:02:44.39,Default,T,0,0,0,,And what's a sports festival, anyway?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:44.39,0:02:47.77,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,You train together as a group \Nto take down formidable foes.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.77,0:02:50.06,Default,K,0,0,0,,Uh, I think there's been \Na miscommunication somewhere.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.06,0:02:53.19,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Kobayashi, you gotta come!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.90,0:02:56.03,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Take down Hades!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:56.03,0:02:57.57,Default,T,0,0,0,,Don't be selfish.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.49,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'll come by myself if I have to.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:59.49,0:03:00.91,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.95,0:03:05.62,Default,T,0,0,0,,What, are you saying you don't want me \Nthere without Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:06.20,0:03:10.92,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Saikawa said everyone would be \Nwith their moms and dads.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.92,0:03:13.29,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,You're like my big sister.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.58,0:03:15.67,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Kobayashi's more like my mom.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:16.80,0:03:20.09,Default,K,0,0,0,split,Your mom? I'm not old enough to—
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.09,0:03:20.68,Default,K,0,0,0,split,Wait...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.97,0:03:25.01,Default,K,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, several of my \Nold classmates actually have kids now.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.81,Default,T,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.22,0:03:28.98,Default,K,0,0,0,,Anyways, I just can't make it.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.98,0:03:31.14,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sorry, but you'll have to settle for Tohru alone.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.48,Default,T,0,0,0,,Settle for me?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.48,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.15,Default,T,0,0,0,,Kanna!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:38.40,0:03:41.82,Default,K,0,0,0,,Is it really that important for a kid's parents to come?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.82,0:03:45.74,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm not even Kanna's mother in the first place.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.74,0:03:50.25,Default,T,0,0,0,,I get the feeling that she's started \Nto look up to you like you are, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.16,0:03:55.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,I can't for the life of me imagine why.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:55.00,0:03:59.17,Default,K,0,0,0,,Besides, neither of my parents \Never came to any of my sports festivals.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.01,Default,K,0,0,0,,They were always busy with work.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:01.38,0:04:04.64,Default,K,0,0,0,,And I understood they had to \Nfocus on keeping the family afloat.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.35,Default,T,0,0,0,,Kanna's parents took a pretty hands-off approach.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.77,Default,T,0,0,0,,They felt a dragon would grow up strong on its own.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.31,0:04:16.52,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's been told countless times \Nto live up to her name of Kanna Kamui.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.11,0:04:22.03,Default,T,0,0,0,,But Kanna kept getting up to mischief \Nto try to get her parents' attention.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.57,0:04:25.03,Default,T,0,0,0,,It escalated until she was banished to this world.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.91,0:04:29.58,Default,T,0,0,0,,I think that's why she wants you to be there for her.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.45,0:04:33.04,Default,K,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to live up to that?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.42,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,Morning, Kanna.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:41.42,0:04:42.72,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.72,0:04:45.72,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Kobayashi's not coming to the sports festival.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.26,Default,S,0,0,0,,Oh, that sucks.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.47,Default,S,0,0,0,,But there's more to a sports festival than that.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.47,0:04:53.73,Default,S,0,0,0,,Working together towards victory \Nis a big part of the fun!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.44,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Victory...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.44,0:04:59.19,Default,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Saikawa's talking about teamwork? \NAre pigs gonna start flying?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.19,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,Shut up! You got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.19,0:05:04.36,Default,Fuku,0,0,0,,Not really, I just don't believe you.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.36,0:05:06.45,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's called having a problem with it!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.03,0:05:08.20,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,A sports festival?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.41,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:09.41,0:05:13.16,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,It totally clashes with our deployment date.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.16,0:05:17.25,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, I don't see why I need to go anyway.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.46,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Do you not want to?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.29,0:05:22.96,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'd like to go if I could, I guess?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.13,0:05:25.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hmm? What's so funny?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:26.05,0:05:29.60,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,I've never seen you worry about something like this before.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.35,Default,K,0,0,0,,You know, you might be right.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.27,0:05:39.11,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,If you ask me, it's more a question of if you {\i1}want{\i0} to go than if you {\i1}can{\i0} go.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.73,Default,K,0,0,0,,If I want to go, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.15,0:05:47.78,Default,T,0,0,0,,Lalala, I'm the cutest maid ever!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.41,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.24,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome home.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.83,Default,T,0,0,0,,Are you still upset, Kanna?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:56.83,0:05:57.67,Default,T,0,0,0,,Cheer up alrea—
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.67,0:06:00.04,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Lady Tohru, perception blocking.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.04,0:06:00.79,Default,T,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.80,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Block perception of me.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.45,0:06:35.33,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.91,Default,T,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.54,Default,T,0,0,0,,Dinner will be ready in a bit.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.63,Default,K,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:42.59,0:06:43.79,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.75,0:06:48.13,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,It's okay if you can't come to the sports festival.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.43,0:06:53.05,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I'll have enough fun working \Ntogether with my classmates.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.05,0:06:56.47,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,So you can just focus on your work.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.98,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, right.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.27,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.77,0:07:08.07,Default,T,0,0,0,,It seems that she went to your workplace \Nand observed you in secret today.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.99,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,What's with this strangely familiar feeling?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.50,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.96,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,It's the same guilt as back then.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:21.92,0:07:22.96,Default,K,0,0,0,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.96,0:07:23.63,Default,T,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.29,0:07:27.13,Default,K,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow, I'll be getting home even later.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.92,Default,T,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.05,Default,T,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.17,Default,Class,0,0,0,,Thirty-five!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.29,Default,Class,0,0,0,,Thirty-six!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.17,Default,Class,0,0,0,,Thirty-seven!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.29,Default,Class,0,0,0,,Thirty-eight!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.29,0:08:08.17,Default,Class,0,0,0,,Thirty-nine!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.13,Default,Class,0,0,0,,For—
Dialogue: 100,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.17,Default,Class,0,0,0,,We were so close!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.59,0:08:15.18,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone. Let's call it a day.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.93,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,You've all learned to jump so many times.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.60,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,I'm so proud of you all!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.60,0:08:23.69,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Keep this up and try to take that gold medal home!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.69,0:08:24.44,Default,All,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.77,0:08:27.02,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,Let's do our best, Kanna.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.94,0:08:28.82,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.53,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Hard at work, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:35.53,0:08:36.70,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.95,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Trying to go to the sports festival?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.95,0:08:39.95,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.24,0:08:41.87,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Realized you wanted to go?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.87,0:08:42.96,Default,K,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.96,0:08:44.96,Default,K,0,0,0,,Realized I {\i1}should{\i0} go.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.34,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Want me to lend you a hand?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.34,0:08:51.01,Default,K,0,0,0,,Huh? Well...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.59,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.60,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,You're picking up the tab next time we go drinking.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.60,0:08:58.85,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.82,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'll be there tomorrow.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.94,0:09:14.82,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.99,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.57,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,You took down Hades?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.45,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.21,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I love you, Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.21,Default - Top,K,0,0,0,,Whoa there.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:25.62,0:09:26.71,Default,T,0,0,0,,My goodness.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.71,Default,T,0,0,0,,Kanna's still such a child.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:34.59,0:09:37.22,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.55,0:09:39.22,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.22,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,I should just take both.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:41.22,0:09:44.68,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,No! I'd go over my daily limit! I can't{mustn't}!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:45.52,0:09:48.23,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,But... still...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.69,Default,Clerk,0,0,0,,Excuse me, ma'am, could you please hurry up?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.98,Default,Elma,0,0,0,joined,I-I know! Just give me a moment!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.91,0:10:06.25,Default - Italic,Teacher,0,0,0,,The 43rd Oborozuka Elementary \NSports Festival will now begin.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.25,0:10:09.25,Default - Italic,Teacher,0,0,0,,Our first event is the Friendship Parade.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.97,Default,T,0,0,0,,Look, there's Kanna!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.97,0:10:23.01,Default,K,0,0,0,,Where? Show me.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.52,Default,T,0,0,0,split,She's looking our way.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.64,Default,T,0,0,0,split,Hey!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.64,0:10:31.02,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah, you always look for family.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:31.77,0:10:32.90,Default,Mother,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.90,0:10:34.28,Default,Nae,0,0,0,,Milady!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:34.28,0:10:36.03,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.03,0:10:39.53,Default,Lucoa,0,0,0,,Shouta!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.91,Default,T,0,0,0,,Looks like Lucoa's here too.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.91,Default - Top,L,0,0,0,,I'm rooting for you!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.66,Default,L,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.74,0:10:51.71,Default,6th Graders,0,0,0,joined,All the participants pledge to uphold \Nthe spirit of sportsmanship,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:51.71,0:10:57.42,Default,6th Graders,0,0,0,,work together with our classmates, \Nand compete fairly to the very end!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:57.92,0:11:03.05,Default - Italic,Teacher,0,0,0,,Next up is the fifth event, \Nthe third-grade three-legged race.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:03.05,0:11:05.06,Default,T,0,0,0,,Kanna, give it your all!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,Don't go overboard!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:06.56,0:11:08.60,Default,Mother,0,0,0,,Riko! Fight!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:08.60,0:11:09.81,Default,Nae,0,0,0,,Best of luck!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.65,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Get set...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:16.36,0:11:18.78,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,L-Let's get our legs tied together, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:18.78,0:11:19.40,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:21.95,0:11:22.95,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Done.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.62,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks, Kanna.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.41,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,We have to link shoulders now.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:27.41,0:11:27.95,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.37,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Next group, get ready.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.71,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Come on, Saikawa. It's our turn.{We're up.}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:40.22,0:11:42.89,Default,S,0,0,0,Split,I-I'm sorry, Kanna.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:42.89,0:11:44.85,Default,S,0,0,0,Split,I was too happy to run.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.60,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,It's okay, Saikawa.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.85,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,There's always next time.{Let's try harder next time.}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:47.85,0:11:50.27,Default,Mother,0,0,0,,Jeez, Riko, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.60,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Discipline!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:52.31,0:11:56.48,Default - Italic,Teacher,0,0,0,,Our seventh event is the fifth-grade scavenger hunt.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.91,Default,L,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.54,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Okay, you pass.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:15.33,0:12:18.09,Default,Student,0,0,0,,Shouta, your sister is amazing!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.84,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:20.26,0:12:23.01,Default - Italic,Teacher,0,0,0,,We will now take a break for lunch.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:23.01,0:12:26.85,Default - Italic,Teacher,0,0,0,,Students and parents, \Nplease enjoy your lunch together.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:27.35,0:12:31.43,Default - Italic,Teacher,0,0,0,,Be careful of heat stroke \Nand be sure to drink plenty of water.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.56,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Looks yummy!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:34.56,0:12:35.85,Default,K,0,0,0,,Wow, it's normal.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:37.11,0:12:39.19,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm not the same dragon I used to be.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.49,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Time to eat.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.36,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Lady Tohru, this is great!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.12,Default,T,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.20,Default,T,0,0,0,split,Here, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.95,Default,T,0,0,0,split,Say "aah."
Dialogue: 100,0:12:48.95,0:12:51.16,Default,K,0,0,0,,Tohru, what kind of meat is this?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.08,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,Knew it.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:56.33,0:12:59.25,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,This lunch really is good.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.67,Default,T,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kanna.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:00.67,0:13:02.92,Default,T,0,0,0,,Eat lots and do your best out there.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:02.92,0:13:03.72,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.63,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Our comeback starts here.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.39,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:15.64,0:13:17.15,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:17.56,0:13:21.90,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,How do you expect me to choose just one \Nfrom over ten different combinations?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:22.19,0:13:24.15,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,I should just get them all.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:24.40,0:13:26.53,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,No! I won't last like that!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.04,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,But... still...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.66,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,Has to be pumpkin and sweet potato.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:32.95,0:13:35.79,Default - Top,Clerk,0,0,0,,Excuse me, ma'am, could you please hurry up?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:34.66,0:13:35.79,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,No, chestnut's hard to pass up.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:36.29,0:13:40.42,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,But they might be onto something \Nwith this unique grape and pear combo!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:40.42,0:13:41.80,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,No, wait! Chest—
Dialogue: 100,0:13:42.84,0:13:46.05,Default - Italic,Teacher,0,0,0,,The afternoon events will now begin.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:46.05,0:13:51.22,Default - Italic,Teacher,0,0,0,,{\q2}Our fifteenth{style guides be damned, this is for consistency} event is the third-grade long-rope jumping.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:51.56,0:13:52.93,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.22,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Ready, start!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:54.22,0:14:01.23,Default - Top,Teacher,0,0,0,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:58.23,0:13:59.73,Default,T,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.23,Default,K,0,0,0,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:01.23,0:14:05.24,Default - Top,Teacher,0,0,0,,8, 9, 10, 11...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.19,Default,Mother,0,0,0,,Riko, fight!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:03.19,0:14:05.24,Default,Nae,0,0,0,,Hang in there, milady!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:05.24,0:14:07.36,Default - Top,T,0,0,0,,22, 23,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:07.36,0:14:12.49,Default - Top,Class 2,0,0,0,,24, 25, 26, 27, 28...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:09.24,0:14:12.49,Default - Italic,Teacher,0,0,0,,Classes 1 and 4 are out.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.50,Default - Top,Both,0,0,0,,42, 43,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:14.50,0:14:19.63,Default - Top,C2,0,0,0,,44, 45, 46, 47, 48...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.04,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,Class 3 is out.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.63,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,Class 2 is amazing. They're still going!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:19.63,0:14:24.63,Default - Top,C2,0,0,0,,55, 56, 57, 58, 59,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:23.63,0:14:24.63,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.63,Default - Top,C2,0,0,0,,60, 61...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:24.63,0:14:25.63,Default,Mother,0,0,0,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.63,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:28.63,0:14:30.76,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,Class 3-2 takes the win!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.14,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,{\an8}They even jumped 61 times!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.14,Default,T,0,0,0,,We won, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:33.85,0:14:36.39,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was impressive.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:37.02,0:14:41.52,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,{\q2}The nineteenth event is the fifth-grade boys cavalry battle.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.77,Default,L,0,0,0,split,Shouta!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.65,Default,L,0,0,0,split,You can do it!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.53,Default,L,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:51.66,0:14:52.24,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.08,Default,C2,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.70,Default,L,0,0,0,,Go, Shouta!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:58.91,0:14:59.92,Default,L,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.46,Default,L,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.84,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:06.84,0:15:09.68,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,Class 3 with an overwhelming victory \Nin the cavalry battle!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:11.34,0:15:14.35,Default,Student,0,0,0,,Shouta, your sister really is amazing!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.56,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:16.22,0:15:20.56,Default - Italic,Teacher,0,0,0,,Our twentieth event is the third-grade tug o' war!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:21.06,0:15:24.02,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Classes 1 and 2, ready...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:26.57,0:15:27.48,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.36,Default,K,0,0,0,,Kanna!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.57,Default,T,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:32.57,0:15:33.99,Default,Mother,0,0,0,,Don't you lose!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:33.99,0:15:34.83,Default,Nae,0,0,0,,Milady!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.67,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,That's it! Class 2 wins!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:49.92,0:15:52.55,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,We did it, Saikawa! We won!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:52.55,0:15:53.80,Default,T,0,0,0,,They did it!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.89,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah, they did well out there.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:55.89,0:15:58.06,Default,T,0,0,0,,Keep the pace up!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:32.13,0:16:35.14,Default,T,0,0,0,,Kanna's class is in second now.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:35.14,0:16:37.26,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah, they'll be in first if they take this next one.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.85,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, it's starting.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:39.43,0:16:43.73,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,{\q2}Our thirty-second event is the third-grade relay race.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:44.85,0:16:48.48,Default,S,0,0,0,,Kanna, let's win this and take first place.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:48.48,0:16:49.36,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:50.07,0:16:53.15,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,This is the final third-grade event.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:53.53,0:16:57.66,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,Let's all cheer for them harder than ever!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.66,Default,Teach,0,0,0,split,Girls' first runners...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.91,Default,Teach,0,0,0,split,On your marks,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:01.54,0:17:02.75,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,get set...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.58,Default,S,0,0,0,,Iida, bring it home!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:05.58,0:17:06.92,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Iida, fight!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:07.21,0:17:09.92,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,All classes have started at the same time.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:09.92,0:17:12.42,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,split,Class 1 currently holds the lead.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:12.42,0:17:15.55,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,split,Classes 2, 4, and 3 follow them in that order.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:18.97,0:17:21.14,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,The baton has been passed to the second runners.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:21.14,0:17:23.48,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,{\an8}Class 1 is keeping the lead.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.48,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Makishima, keep it up!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.27,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Saikawa, you can do it.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.73,Default,S,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:27.73,0:17:30.15,Default,S,0,0,0,,I'll be in the lead when I pass you the baton.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:30.52,0:17:33.40,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,Classes 1 and 2 are locked in a dead heat!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.82,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,Give it your all, everyone!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:38.66,0:17:40.03,Default,S,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:40.95,0:17:43.62,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,Whoa, Class 2 is gaining quickly!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:43.62,0:17:46.29,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,They've now passed up Class 1!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.00,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,Split,Oh no!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:50.00,0:17:52.88,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,Split,Class 2 has dropped its baton!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:06.44,0:18:08.90,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,Now in the lead is Class 1.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:08.90,0:18:12.36,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,Classes 4, 3, and 2 follow them in that order.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.00,Default,S,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:25.91,0:18:27.00,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.47,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,The anchors have started their leg.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:37.47,0:18:39.76,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,Class 2's is unbelievably fast!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.85,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,She's passing the others in rapid succession!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.69,Default,S,0,0,0,,Kanna...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:54.69,0:18:55.94,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Just one more!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.19,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Keep running!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:59.45,0:19:00.45,Default,Class 2,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:04.45,0:19:06.45,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,Goal!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:06.45,0:19:08.46,Default - Italic,Teach,0,0,0,,Class 2 takes the victory!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:08.46,0:19:09.96,Default,Class2,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.21,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Kanna!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:16.67,0:19:18.17,Default,Iida,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Kanna!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:18.17,0:19:19.93,Default,Shima,0,0,0,,You were so cool!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.85,Default,S,0,0,0,,K-Kanna?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.39,Default,S,0,0,0,Split,Um, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:27.39,0:19:28.56,Default,S,0,0,0,Split,I messed up!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:30.39,0:19:34.61,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,We only won because you closed the gap as much as you did.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:36.53,0:19:38.24,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Thanks, Saikawa.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:41.24,0:19:43.24,Default,S,0,0,0,,Kanna!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:04.39,0:20:06.39,Default,K,0,0,0,,Great job today, Kanna.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:07.26,0:20:09.06,Default,K,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You did great out there.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:13.15,0:20:17.40,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Yeah. We won because we all worked together.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:17.73,0:20:21.65,Default,T,0,0,0,,But you must be at least a little frustrated you couldn't go all out.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.61,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,Split,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:23.61,0:20:25.41,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,Split,I had fun with everyone.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:27.08,0:20:28.66,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.91,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming today.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:36.75,0:20:38.46,Default,K,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:39.50,0:20:42.22,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,You too, Lady Tohru. Thanks for lunch.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:42.22,0:20:43.55,Default,T,0,0,0,,You're very welcome.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.43,Default,T,0,0,0,,It was my pleasure.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:46.80,0:20:49.81,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,Attending a sports festival as a guardian, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:50.14,0:20:52.85,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,How my life has changed.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:54.52,0:20:58.06,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,Did I change myself at some point?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:00.23,0:21:04.32,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,But I do want to let loose today.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:04.61,0:21:05.82,Default,T,0,0,0,,Go figure.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:05.82,0:21:08.03,Default,T,0,0,0,,{\q2}What do you say we go at it, Kanna? It's been a while.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:08.41,0:21:09.66,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Bring it.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.62,Default,L,0,0,0,,Let me in on the fun!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:11.62,0:21:14.33,Default,T,0,0,0,,Great! Let's face off in a triple threat!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:14.33,0:21:15.12,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:15.12,0:21:17.13,Default,T,0,0,0,,May we, Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:17.13,0:21:20.88,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sure, as long as you don't cause any trouble.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:21.17,0:21:22.92,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Where should we do it, Lady Tohru?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:22.92,0:21:25.34,Default,T,0,0,0,,The usual place should do.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.01,Default,K,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:26.01,0:21:26.89,Default,L,0,0,0,,I'm itching to go!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:38.44,0:21:40.44,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,Which one should I pick?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:40.44,0:21:42.44,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,Which one should I pick?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:42.73,0:21:44.19,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,Which one should I...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:44.19,0:21:45.57,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,Which one...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:48.03,0:21:51.99,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,Why do human creations force me to make such difficult choices?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:52.24,0:21:55.00,Default - Italic,Elma,0,0,0,,Humans are terrifying!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:26.59,0:23:29.30,Default,J,0,0,0,,I'm Georgie, the Saikawa family maid.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:29.76,0:23:32.64,Default,L,0,0,0,,I'm Lucoa, Shouta's familiar.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:32.64,0:23:34.22,Default,J,0,0,0,,Familiar?
Dialogue: 100,0:23:34.22,0:23:35.01,Default,L,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:35.01,0:23:38.35,Default,J,0,0,0,,It seems we both have rather unique tastes.
