Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.00,0:01:16.46,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}Tell me, how did I get here?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.46,0:01:18.42,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(120,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}I only made one tiny-winey mistake
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.42,0:01:22.13,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(210,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}and now I'm at a ta-la-la ta-la-ta total loss
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.13,0:01:23.63,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}Why now of all times
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.63,0:01:25.43,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}did I grow a spine and stick around?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.43,0:01:28.97,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}Somehow I've been taken by whimsy
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.97,0:01:31.22,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}with no choice but to sing along
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.22,0:01:34.56,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}That's just how it is at first,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.56,0:01:38.23,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}feeling like you're not in control
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.23,0:01:41.78,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}But if you open up and listen...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.78,0:01:46.91,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(180,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}that's your voice saying, "Come on! Let's go!"
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.91,0:01:48.66,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}(Anywhere is fine!)
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.66,0:01:55.54,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,160)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}I have the courage to become your wings
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.54,0:01:59.09,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(120,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}I'll take on the world without any fear
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.09,0:02:03.01,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(220,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}as long as I feel this magic
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.01,0:02:09.80,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(120,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}A bouquet for this unfamiliar world,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.80,0:02:13.68,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(170,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}wrapped up together in this moment
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.68,0:02:15.35,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}We communicate on different levels,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.35,0:02:17.23,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}but it doesn't bother me one bit
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.23,0:02:19.65,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,240)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}so long as this peace lasts forevermore
