Comment: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:16.46,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}Tell me, how did I get here?
Comment: 0,0:01:16.46,0:01:18.42,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I only made one tiny-winey mistake
Comment: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:22.13,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}and now I'm at a ta-la-la ta-la-ta total loss
Comment: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:23.63,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}Why now of all times
Comment: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:25.43,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}did I grow a spine and stick around?
Comment: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:28.97,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}Somehow I've been taken by whimsy
Comment: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:31.22,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}with no choice but to sing along
Comment: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:34.56,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}That's just how it is at first,
Comment: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:38.23,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}feeling like you're not in control
Comment: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:41.78,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}But if you open up and listen...
Comment: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:46.91,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}that's your voice saying, "Come on! Let's go!"
Comment: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:48.66,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}(Anywhere is fine!)
Comment: 0,0:01:48.66,0:01:55.54,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I have the courage to become your wings
Comment: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:59.09,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I'll take on the world without any fear
Comment: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:03.01,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}as long as I feel this magic
Comment: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:09.80,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}A bouquet for this unfamiliar world,
Comment: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:13.68,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}wrapped up together in this moment
Comment: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:15.35,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}We communicate on different levels,
Comment: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:17.23,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}but it doesn't bother me one bit
Comment: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:19.65,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}so long as this peace lasts forevermore
